%e A049800 Array T(n,k) (with rows n >= 1 and columns k >= 1) begins as follows:
%e A049800   0;
%e A049800   0, 0;
%e A049800   0, 0, 0;
%e A049800   0, 0, 1, 1;
%e A049800   0, 0, 0, 0, 0;
